elements.name: Verifying Adactin Book Hotel By Select All Fileds

steps.name: User is on the adactin Page
User should verify welcome message after login "Hello gokulmgn!"
User should perform the search hotel "London","Hotel Sunshine","Double","1 - One","20/12/2022","21/12/2022","2 - Two" and "2 - Two"
User should verify after the select hotel title "Select Hotel" in the select hotel page
User should select the Hotel Name and Click Continue button
User should verify after select hotel title "Book A Hotel" in the book hotel page
User should Enter all fileds "GOKUL","M" and "CHENNAI" in book hotel page
